title: God Will Finish What He Started | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: God Will Finish What He Started | Joel Osteen
description:
Whatever God starts in your life, He will finish. Stay in faith. The moment He put that dream in your heart, He set its completion date!


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
